						<h2>Chris Noden
							<span>Chief Technical Officer</span>
						</h2>
						<p>
							Chris has a broad and deep background in technology - rooted in new media, content delivery,
							licensing, compliance and agile development. Chris was founding Technical Manager at Monstermob
							taking them from their first platform through to flotation on the London Stock Exchange. He has
							also held senior roles at DX3 Technologies, Urban Mobile, Promotion Space Group and has consulted
							to Datz, Three, Tesco Mobile &amp; Trinity Mirror to name a few.
						</p>
						<p>
							Chris heads up the MOFILM design &amp; development team and is leading the charge to provide MOFILM
							with the best technology in the business.
						</p>

